  "title": "A Casual Encounter with Han Solo",
  "summary": "On a residential avenue in Capital City on Etti IV, Piper steps out to walk her unruly labrador, Duke, who strains toward a nearby park. The smuggler Han Solo strolls casually through the area, keeping a low profile, until Duke breaks free and bounds over to him, refusing to leave the stranger alone despite Piper's embarrassed scolding. Piper apologizes for the dog's behavior and the two exchange light, guarded small talk, with Han claiming to be just passing through while Piper recommends the planet's shops. The encounter stays cordial and inconsequential, and Han eventually melts back into the crowd while Piper lets Duke lead her off toward the park. Nothing is resolved or revealed, but the brush with the famous Corellian leaves a faint impression.",
